NT|^z@3^b@2^^|cp|8|AT|^B@2^*Bhondo717:   ^*N|cp||at|However, after the 2nd diamond finesse, at trick thee, I probably play a club to the queen just to guarantee a 2nd club trick. In that case north ends up perhaps making 6. North can finesse the @CJ when the @CQ wins.|
