NT|^z@3^b@2^^|cp|8|AT|^B@2^*Bhondo717:   ^*N|cp||at|The reason for club to the queen isn't because the @CJ happens to be onside. It is because I want to make sure to generate a sure club trick and I don't want to have a diamond come back and end up losing a diamond unnecessarily by knocking out the @CA.|
